Summary: Watched 3 start then move some distance then stop
divs: Sighting DetailsI was viewing Orions Nebulae at 2:15 am through my telescope. I thought the number of stars to be strange meaning there seemed to be more stars then there's supposed to be. Then 3 "stars" or UFO's just started to move in a westerly direction. Moving slowly for 10 minutes or so. All 3 just started to slow down then they all stopped at once. I sat there for a few more minutes to see if anything else would happen but nothing did so I went to bed.
